<figcaption class="">Taking off. Henry my neighbor（荷兰），设计师：Mariken Wessels, Jurgen Maelfeyt</figcaption></figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://yellowmedotbe.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/daniel2.jpg">yellowme.be</a> 、<a href="http://www.stiftung-buchkunst.de/en/best-book-design-from-all-over-the-world/2016/honorary-appreciations.html">Stiftung Buchkunst</a></p>
